file.content:
openapi: 3.0.0
info:
  title: Simple API overview
  version: 1.0.0
paths:
  "/test":
    get:
      responses:
        "200":
          description: the user being returned
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                type: object
                properties:
                  uuid:
                    type: string
                    format: uuid
          links:
            address:
              operationId: getUserAddress
              parameters:
                userId: $request.path.id
  "/users/{userid}/address":
    parameters:
      - name: userid
        in: path
        required: true
        description: the user identifier, as userId
        schema:
          type: string
    get:
      operationId: getUserAdsssdress
      responses:
        "200":
          description: the user's address
